@startuml
title <font size=12>Admin - Riwayat Transaksi Flow (Edit Only)</font>

actor Admin
participant Browser
participant TransaksiController
participant Database
participant ActivityLogService

== View Transaksi ==
Admin -> Browser: Akses Riwayat Transaksi
Browser -> TransaksiController: GET /admin/riwayat-transaksi/filters
TransaksiController -> Database: Load transaksi dengan filter tanggal
Database -> TransaksiController: Return data transaksi
TransaksiController -> Browser: Display daftar transaksi
Browser -> Admin: Tampilkan daftar dengan tombol Edit & Detail

== Edit Transaksi ==
Admin -> Browser: Klik tombol Edit
Browser -> TransaksiController: GET /admin/riwayat-transaksi/{id}/edit
TransaksiController -> Database: Load transaksi + detail items
Database -> TransaksiController: Return transaksi & barang info
TransaksiController -> Browser: Display form edit dengan qty items
Browser -> Admin: Ubah jumlah item
Admin -> Browser: Ubah quantity dan submit
Browser -> TransaksiController: PUT /admin/riwayat-transaksi/{id}
TransaksiController -> Database: Start Transaction
Database -> TransaksiController: Transaction started
TransaksiController -> Database: Validate stok untuk qty baru
Database -> TransaksiController: Stock check result
TransaksiController -> Database: Update detail_transaksi qty
TransaksiController -> Database: Update stok barang (increment/decrement)
TransaksiController -> Database: Calculate new total
TransaksiController -> Database: Update transaksi total_harga
ActivityLogService -> Database: Insert activity log (perubahan)
Database -> ActivityLogService: Activity logged
TransaksiController -> Database: Commit Transaction
Database -> TransaksiController: Transaction committed
TransaksiController -> Browser: Redirect ke invoice dengan success message
Browser -> Admin: Show update success
@enduml
